1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
Why do you feel guilty doing nothing?

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:04,240
Honestly, it's not even you.

3
00:00:04,240 --> 00:00:06,560
A few hundred years ago, as factories took over,

4
00:00:06,560 --> 00:00:08,280
a new idea got sold.

5
00:00:08,280 --> 00:00:11,560
Hard work is holy, and rest is wasted time.

6
00:00:11,560 --> 00:00:15,240
So, resting got quietly rebranded as a moral failure.

7
00:00:15,240 --> 00:00:18,920
That guilt in your chest is basically a very old sales pitch,

8
00:00:18,920 --> 00:00:20,440
but that's only half the story.
